1
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:24,000
You're injured.

2
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:25,000
Press it like this.

3
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:26,000
Tian.

4
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:27,000
Yang.

5
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:28,000
Come here.

6
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:31,000
You stay here to serve Mr. Tian.

7
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:34,000
Mother, you know that I don't like this thing.

8
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:35,000
I won't be able to find the thing you like.

9
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:36,000
Okay, Mother.
I won't be able to find the thing you like.

10
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:36,500
Okay, Mother.

11
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:37,000
You fear of losing power,
Okay, Mother.

12
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:40,000
losing the leadership of the family because of having a son like me.

13
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Do you remember Lady Pin?

14
00:00:43,300 --> 00:00:45,000
Mr. Song ordered his son to get married before succeeding.

15
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:47,000
So she immediately looked for a woman for her son.

16
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:50,000
She picked Lady Pin, the daughter of Prince Pat.

17
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:51,000
I must prevent her no matter what.

18
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:55,000
You want to destroy the wedding and find out their secret at the same time.

19
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,000
Will you be successful?

20
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:58,500
Tian.

21
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:01,000
You're forcing me too much.

22
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:02,000
If I didn't force you,

23
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:04,000
everyone would know the truth by now.

24
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:08,000
Sometimes I want everyone to know the truth.

25
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,000
What's wrong?

26
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:21,000
I don't want to discuss about this with you anymore.

27
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,000
Tian.

28
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,000
We haven't finished talking yet.

29
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:43,000
I didn't really eavesdrop on you.

30
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,000
I searched for Nuan there because I thought she was inside.

31
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,000
Why would Nuan come to my room?

32
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,000
Right.

33
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:53,000
Why did you come into Tian's room?

34
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,000
I didn't.

35
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,000
Well, she didn't enter your room, but I think she did.

36
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:00,000
Enough, Mom.

37
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:03,000
Do you have to do this out of curiosity?

38
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:06,000
You even sneaked into Tian's room.

39
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,000
You're not embarrassed but I am.

40
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,000
Enough, Yang.

41
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,000
I apologize on behalf of my mother.

42
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,000
Stop please.

43
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,000
Aunt Chan.

44
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:20,000
Don't do this again.

45
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,000
That's enough.

46
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,000
I'm not angry anymore.

47
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:25,000
Don't scold your mom.

48
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,000
See?

49
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,000
You see that Tian isn't mad at me at all.

50
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,000
But you keep scolding me.

51
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:35,000
You still don't get it? Tian is too kind.

52
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,000
You're lucky that he didn't tell Madam.

53
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:42,000
If it was me, I'd tell Madam to deal with you.

54
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,000
Are you my son or my father?

55
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,000
I'd better tell Madam.

56
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,000
No, no, please.

57
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,000
You.

58
00:04:52,500 --> 00:04:53,000
Alright.

59
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,000
Tian, I'm sorry.

60
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,000
Okay.

61
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:18,000
I heard that Madam brought a woman to Mr. Tian.

62
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:20,000
Did anybody see what she looks like?

63
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,000
Is she pretty?

64
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,000
Me, me.

65
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:25,000
Lady Pin is beautiful, cute and sweet.

66
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,000
As expected from a noble family member.

67
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:30,000
I think she's the best suited for our Mr. Tian.

68
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:35,000
The one you told me that her father has given the palace as a pledge?

69
00:05:35,300 --> 00:05:36,000
Yes.

70
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:39,000
So this is called getting married to pay off debts.

71
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:43,000
But they are a good match anyway.

72
00:05:43,500 --> 00:05:44,000
You give up.

73
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:47,000
Everyone knows that you are aiming for Mr. Tian.

74
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,000
You have no more hope.

75
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:54,000
I didn't aim to be Mr. Tian's first wife.

76
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:56,000
Being a second wife is enough.

77
00:05:57,000 --> 00:06:00,000
Don't talk to her. Let her in her daydream.

78
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:59,000
How is it, Commander?

79
00:06:59,500 --> 00:07:03,000
It let the girls change into kimonos to please you.

80
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,000
Do you like it?

81
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,000
Yes, pretty.

82
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:09,000
Pretty.

83
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:13,000
But not as pretty as the Japanese women in my country.

84
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:19,000
Then go back to your home, Jap.

85
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:20,000
What did you say?

86
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:24,000
Cheers.

87
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,000
Cheers.

88
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:48,000
Chinese and Thais don't have money to come here.

89
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,000
Only these guys.

90
00:07:50,700 --> 00:07:52,000
Every time they come, they never pay a penny.

91
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:55,000
Before the war is over, my restaurant may have gone bust.

92
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,000
Don't be so upset, Madam.

93
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,000
So do you got anything?

94
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:24,000
Not yet, Madam.

95
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:29,000
In times of war like this, only the Japanese visit us.

96
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,000
They didn't pay enough.

97
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:36,000
Mr. Ma also seemed to plan to gobble up our teahouse.

98
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:40,000
If someone knows that I have borrowed money to support it,

99
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:43,000
Cai family will definitely be kicked out of the Five Dragons Association.

100
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:46,000
Don't worry about it, Madam.

101
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:49,000
I will find a way to sleep with Mr. Tian as soon as possible.

102
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,000
If I become his wife,

103
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:55,000
I can ask him to help support your teahouse.

104
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:58,000
No one would dare to stop the head of the Five Dragons Association.

105
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,000
I hope so.

106
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:05,000
These days, when I attend the meeting of Five Dragons Association,

107
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:07,000
no one respects me

108
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,000
or care about me.

109
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:10,000
It's because I am a woman.

110
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,000
No one listens to me when I give opinion.

111
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,000
Worthless.

112
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,000
Madam.

113
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,000
You are a kind-hearted person.

114
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,000
You are valuable to everyone here.

115
00:09:22,700 --> 00:09:25,000
The day that I had nothing to eat and no place to sleep.

116
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:28,000
There were only you who took care of me.

117
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:33,000
And what happened at the Song family?

118
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:38,000
Now, Madam Li has found a woman for Mr. Tian.

119
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:40,000
I heard that they will get married soon.

120
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:44,000
That's no big deal.

121
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,000
If you have a chance to serve Tian,

122
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,000
I'm confident that

123
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:55,000
any man who sleeps with you will be fascinated.

124
00:09:56,000 --> 00:10:00,000
Apply all the tricks I trained you.

125
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,000
Yes, Madam.

126
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:06,000
I must turn Mr. Tian into my husband.

127
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,000
I won't let our sisters starve to death.

128
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:13,000
Aunt Jia who usually interfered me doesn't dare to do the same.

129
00:10:13,500 --> 00:10:14,000
Because previously,

130
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,000
Madam Li has allowed me to approach Mr. Tian.

131
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:20,000
Madam Li has allowed you to approach Tian?

132
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:21,000
Right.

133
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,000
That's strange.

134
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:28,000
A woman like Li loves Tian and treats him like mama's boy.

135
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:31,000
You have to be careful.

136
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,000
I think there's something strange about it.

137
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,000
Yes, Madam.

138
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:47,000
This is the tea that I bought back from abroad.

139
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:49,000
I'd like to give it to you.

140
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,000
Thanks a lot.

141
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:52,000
You are very kind.

142
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:57,000
So isn't Tian home?

143
00:10:58,000 --> 00:11:00,000
I want to ask him to accompany me to a coffee shop.

144
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:03,000
The shop is around the palace.

145
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:08,000
He's there.

146
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:09,000
Tian.

147
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,000
Come here.

148
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,000
Hello, Tian.

149
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:19,000
Hi.

150
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:22,000
Pin visits me to give me a gift.

151
00:11:22,500 --> 00:11:24,000
She wants to invite you to drink coffee.

152
00:11:24,500 --> 00:11:25,000
But I…

153
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:29,000
I've promised her that you will accompany her.

154
00:11:29,500 --> 00:00:35,000
So you want me to break my word?

155
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:49,000
Am I bothering you?

156
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:50,000
Not at all.

157
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,000
Please.

158
00:11:52,700 --> 00:11:53,000
Where are you going?

159
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:57,000
Pin, Tian.

160
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:02,000
We're going to run errands. Excuse me.

161
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,000
Let's go, Tian.

162
00:12:04,300 --> 00:12:05,000
Can I go with you?

163
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,000
I said we were running errands.

164
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,000
Don't you understand?

165
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:20,000
If you don't let me join,

166
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,000
I will tell Tian

167
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:25,000
that the two of us have met before.

168
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,000
Tian.

169
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:30,000
You can come with us.

170
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,000
More people would be fun.

171
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,000
Then let's go.

172
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,000
Are you ready?

173
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,000
Yes.

174
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,000
Let's go.

175
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,000
This dessert is yummy, Tian.

176
00:13:28,300 --> 00:13:29,000
Take a bite.

177
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,000
Thanks.

178
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:35,000
Let me try.

179
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:42,000
Wow.

180
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:45,000
Tian, this is very delicious.

181
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,000
Next bite.

182
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,000
One more bite.

183
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:32,000
Tian.

184
00:14:32,300 --> 00:14:33,000
Did you meet an acquaintance?

185
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:37,000
Yang, stay here with Pin. I'll be right back.

186
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,000
Tian.

187
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,000
Young man.

188
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,000
I'm sorry.

189
00:15:38,300 --> 00:15:39,000
It's okay.

190
00:15:39,300 --> 00:15:40,000
It's okay.

191
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:44,000
It's okay. That's fine.

192
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,000
Pin.

193
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,000
Lady Pin, you'll hurt your neck.

194
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,000
My brother will be back soon.

195
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,000
But actually,

196
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,000
it's good we're alone.

197
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,000
So we can discuss now.

198
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:24,000
What discuss? I have nothing to discuss with you.

199
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,000
Nothing to talk to me?

200
00:16:26,500 --> 00:16:28,000
Can you talk to me nicely?

201
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:31,000
In fact, you should have made friends with me.

202
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:34,000
I'm Tian's beloved brother.

203
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:36,000
He believes whatever I say.

204
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:39,000
Maybe I can help you.

205
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:42,000
You will help me?

206
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:46,000
I could obviously see that you always disturb me and Tian.

207
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:49,000
Otherwise you probably won't come with us today.

208
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,000
Or...

209
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,000
Did you change your mind?

210
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:57,000
You want some benefits in exchange.

211
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:00,000
Speak up.

212
00:17:00,300 --> 00:17:01,000
Maybe I can give it to you.

213
00:17:01,700 --> 00:17:03,000
Me want something from you?

214
00:17:03,700 --> 00:17:07,000
I did everything because I want to protect my brother.

215
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:10,000
I've probed into your family background.

216
00:17:10,700 --> 00:17:13,000
And I know how your family status is now.

217
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:17,000
Your palace is now mortgaged to Madam Li.

218
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:21,000
If you marry Tian, everything will be solved, right?

219
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:24,000
Aunt Li approves the relationship between me and Tian.

220
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,000
Do you think you can stop it?

221
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:29,000
I know that it's difficult, so I want to talk to you first.

222
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:31,000
My brother is a good man.

223
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:34,000
I want him to love and end up with someone he pleases.

224
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:36,000
Not being forced like this.

225
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:39,000
And how about you?

226
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,000
Are you forced or are you happy with it?

227
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,000
If it is the first,

228
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:45,000
I want you to go on and follow what you want.

229
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:49,000
But if it's the latter, then it's unfortunate

230
00:17:49,500 --> 00:17:52,000
that someone who is well-educated like you

231
00:17:52,600 --> 00:17:54,000
are willing to trade everything and your own happiness for money.

232
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:57,000
I think it's embarrassing and lacking of dignity.

233
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:02,000
Wait. Lady Pin.

234
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:04,000
Pin.

235
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:07,000
Pin.

236
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:12,000
You slip again.

237
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,000
Are you alright?

238
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,000
Let me help.

239
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:22,000
Leave me alone.

240
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:29,000
Yang.

241
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:31,000
Yang.

242
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:35,000
Hey, let me down.

243
00:18:35,100 --> 00:18:36,000
Stay sill.

244
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:42,000
Sit here.

245
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,000
Excuse me.

246
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:03,000
Does this hurt?

247
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,000
Is it better?

248
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:25,000
I'm sorry when I spoke badly to you.

249
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:30,000
I'm always like this, doing whatever I want.

250
00:19:30,700 --> 00:19:32,000
I just want you to give it a try.

251
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:37,000
How happy it is to be able to do what you want.

252
00:19:38,600 --> 00:19:41,000
You can say that because you don't have anything to carry.

253
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:45,000
If you don't understand what I'm saying,

254
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:48,000
think of your brother.

255
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:51,000
I and Tian,

256
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:57,000
We are forced to do something to protect the honor of our family.

257
00:19:58,000 --> 00:20:00,000
If we can choose,

258
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:03,000
we would have done everything according to our own will.

259
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:05,000
No one wants to be tired of carrying all the burdens.

260
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:14,000
Be careful.

261
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:20,000
I may have no dignity as you said.

262
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:23,000
But I will do my best.

263
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:27,000
No matter how you intervene, I don't care.

264
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:32,000
Tell Tian that I have some business, I'll leave first.

265
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:49,000
You.

266
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:02,000
That's blood.

267
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:17,000
This is the wound you got from helping me the other day.

268
00:23:17,300 --> 00:23:18,000
Didn't you go to the doctor?

269
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:20,000
The wound is inflamed.

270
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:39,000
And are the Japanese soldiers still following you?

271
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,000
If they follow you,

272
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:44,000
I can help you find a place to hide.

273
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:46,000
You can come stay at my house.

274
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:49,000
My house is near Song family's warehouse pier.

275
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:52,000
Or if you have trouble or need something,

276
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:54,000
you can visit me at home.

277
00:23:58,000 --> 00:24:03,000
I just want to repay the gratitude that you have saved me.

278
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:07,000
Thanks.

279
00:24:10,000 --> 00:24:11,000
Wait.

280
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:16,000
My name is Tian.

281
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:18,000
Your name is…

282
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:21,000
I think you shouldn't know.

283
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:24,000
We are not destined to meet each other.

284
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:27,000
Whenever we meet, there is always injury.

285
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:19,000
Thank you.

286
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,000
Tian.

287
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:34,000
Yang.

288
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:43,000
Well, I met someone who helped me the other day.

289
00:25:43,400 --> 00:25:44,000
So I follow to thank him.

290
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:45,000
Do you play the heroine?

291
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:59,000
Did I tell you?

292
00:26:59,500 --> 00:27:02,000
If anyone knows this, you will be in trouble.

293
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:03,000
Remember it. Remember it.

294
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:04,500
Madam, please stop.

295
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:07,000
Madam, please. Mr. Tian will die.

296
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:16,000
Emperor Ai of Han

297
00:27:16,500 --> 00:27:20,000
saw his lover was still asleep on his sleeve.

298
00:27:20,800 --> 00:27:24,000
So he cut off his sleeve rather

299
00:27:24,800 --> 00:27:26,000
than disturb the sleeping of Dong Xian,

300
00:27:26,500 --> 00:27:30,000
so that his lover could continue sleep comfortably.

301
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:33,000
People use this word

302
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:37,000
to refer to a man who loves another man.

303
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:41,000
Or we call them gay.

304
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:44,000
Tian.

305
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:12,000
Yang.

306
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:24,000
What's wrong with you?

307
00:28:27,000 --> 00:28:28,000
Nothing.

308
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:30,000
I just want to hug you.

309
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:36,000
Father has scolded you so you want me to help, right?

310
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,000
Tian.

311
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:43,000
Are you tired?

312
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:54,000
If I say I'm tired,

313
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:58,000
will you change your mind to learn the job and help me and Father?

314
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:05,000
You have to carry a lot.

315
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:08,000
No matter what,

316
00:29:09,700 --> 00:29:12,000
I want you to know that I'm always beside you.

317
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:16,000
I'll be your same old brother, Tian.

318
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:20,000
I know that.

319
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:24,000
So are you going to tell me now

320
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:26,000
what Father scold you?

321
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:33,000
Mr. Ma is getting overconfident.

322
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:36,000
And what are you going to do?

323
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:40,000
I think we should attack him quickly.

324
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:43,000
Don't let anyone catch you.

325
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:45,000
Yes, sir.

326
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:21,000
I've done what you told me.

327
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:27,000
Good.

328
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:30,000
That cop deserves to die.

329
00:31:30,500 --> 00:31:33,000
He received quite a lot of bribe from me.

330
00:31:33,700 --> 00:31:36,000
He was still greedy for more money.

331
00:31:37,000 --> 00:31:40,000
He once contacted my business competitor

332
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:42,000
to tell my business secret.

333
00:31:42,700 --> 00:31:46,000
Luckily, my spy reported me first.

334
00:31:46,700 --> 00:31:48,000
If he succeeded,

335
00:31:48,700 --> 00:31:51,000
my business would have been affected a lot.

336
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:55,000
You did great.

337
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:58,000
When will you work for me officially?

338
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:02,000
I don't like commitment.

339
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:04,000
I'd rather take each job.

340
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:08,000
That's fine.

341
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:13,000
I don't want to force anyone.
So you'll be better.

342
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:16,000
How is your sister's condition?

343
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:22,000
Since she got the medicine from you, her condition is improving.

344
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:27,000
Here.

345
00:32:31,000 --> 00:32:32,000
Take more of it.

346
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:35,000
If you run out of medicine and need more,

347
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:37,000
come find me.

348
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:41,000
Thank you, Mr. Ma.

349
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:55,000
How are you?

350
00:32:55,300 --> 00:32:56,000
Is it still painful?

351
00:32:56,500 --> 00:32:58,000
After you let me take the medicine you brought,

352
00:32:59,000 --> 00:33:01,000
the pain has improved a lot.

353
00:33:01,700 --> 00:33:04,000
No joint pain and bone pain like before.

354
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:06,000
That's good.

355
00:33:07,000 --> 00:32:12,000
If I work and save a lot of money
I'll take you to a good doctor.

356
00:33:19,000 --> 00:33:21,000
Jiu is not tired. He's good at it.

357
00:33:21,600 --> 00:33:23,000
When I grow up, I want to be like Jiu.

358
00:33:23,500 --> 00:33:25,000
Then I will help you find money to heal Mei.

359
00:33:26,000 --> 00:33:27,000
I will work hard.

360
00:33:27,600 --> 00:33:30,000
And if I'm rich, I'll take everyone on a trip around the country.

361
00:33:30,500 --> 00:33:31,000
Is it good?

362
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:55,000
You're injured.

363
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:00,000
Press it like this.

364
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:32,000
My name is Tian.

365
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,000
Done?

366
00:34:51,000 --> 00:34:52,000
So fast.

367
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:55,000
Tian.

368
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:57,000
You're here. Come here, son.

369
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:04,000
I have good news for you.

370
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,000
Li and I are able to find you an auspicious date.

371
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:12,000
Auspicious date?

372
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:14,000
For Wedding?

373
00:35:14,300 --> 00:35:15,000
Right.

374
00:35:16,000 --> 00:35:20,000
Mother said that you're very fond of Lady Pin

375
00:35:20,700 --> 00:35:22,000
and want to get married soon.

376
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:26,000
So I let the fortune teller to find you an auspicious date.

377
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:28,000
Mother.

378
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:35,000
Well, I've thought about it carefully,

379
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:38,000
I'm not in a hurry.

380
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:41,000
So what are you waiting for?

381
00:35:41,700 --> 00:35:43,000
If you love each other, then get married quickly.

382
00:35:44,000 --> 00:35:45,000
So you'll have children earlier.

383
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:50,000
I want to work first.

384
00:35:50,500 --> 00:35:53,000
As for marriage, we can just date.

385
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:55,000
Tian.

386
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:57,000
According to tradition,

387
00:35:58,000 --> 00:36:00,000
you have to get married before assuming the position.

388
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:04,000
You can still work after getting married.

389
00:36:11,000 --> 00:36:13,000
It's okay, son.

390
00:36:13,300 --> 00:36:15,000
Don't hurry.

391
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:16,000
You can date first.

392
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:19,000
Because you have to get married anyway.

393
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:37,000
Mr. Tian seems to be dissatisfied with Madam Li that she speeds up the wedding.

394
00:36:37,700 --> 00:36:40,000
Looks like they're definitely arguing.

395
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:42,000
So why didn't you listen until the end?

396
00:36:43,700 --> 00:36:47,000
I hurried back and reported to you.

397
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:48,000
Let's go, let's listen.

398
00:36:49,000 --> 00:36:50,000
Wait.

399
00:36:50,600 --> 00:36:54,000
Mr. Tian just caught you eavesdropping in the closet.

400
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:56,000
Don't let him catch you again.

401
00:36:57,000 --> 00:36:58,000
Yes, Madam.

402
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,000
Mother.

403
00:37:01,000 --> 00:37:02,000
Mother.

404
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:11,000
You've gone overboard.

405
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:14,000
You even lied to Father to speed up the wedding.

406
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:17,000
Why do you have to do this?

407
00:37:17,500 --> 00:37:18,000
So what are you waiting for?

408
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:21,000
Waiting for everyone to know what you are?

409
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:24,000
Or waiting for Chan to push her son to take your position?

410
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:27,000
I just ask for some time.

411
00:37:29,000 --> 00:37:30,000
I know that I have to get married,

412
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:32,000
to succeed the position.

413
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:35,000
But this is too soon, Mother.

414
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:36,000
The faster, the better.

415
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:39,000
Once you officially take possession of everything,

416
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:43,000
you can be anything and no one dared to talk bad about you.

417
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:45,000
So you mean…

418
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:48,000
if I get married and succeed Father,

419
00:37:48,500 --> 00:37:50,000
I can be anything I like?

420
00:37:50,700 --> 00:37:53,000
Just don't let anyone know what you are.

421
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:59,000
Please listen to your mother, Mr. Tian.

422
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:05,000
I have to live a life as a good son.

423
00:38:05,700 --> 00:38:09,000
I have to cover up and lie for the rest of my life, right?

424
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:13,000
Not forever, Tian.

425
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:16,000
Even though you are like this,

426
00:38:16,500 --> 00:38:19,000
But I've heard that a person of your type

427
00:38:19,700 --> 00:38:22,000
can get married and have heirs.

428
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:24,000
And if you have an heir…

429
00:38:24,100 --> 00:38:24,800
Yes, Mother.

430
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:28,000
A homosexual like me can have an heir.

431
00:38:28,300 --> 00:38:31,000
But I don't want to, Mother. I don't want to get married.

432
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:39,000
Mr. Tian is homosexual. He's gay.

433
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:41,000
Oh my god.

434
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:46,000
Who is it?

435
00:39:05,000 --> 00:39:06,000
Mr. Tian is homosexual.

436
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:08,000
He likes men?

437
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:06,000
If this leaks out,

438
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:08,000
they will be screwed.

439
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:28,000
Where does that mother and son go fighting?

440
00:40:29,000 --> 00:40:32,000
Nuan, you should follow them.

441
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:33,000
See? We miss them.

442
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:38,000
Madam Chan.

443
00:40:38,500 --> 00:40:39,000
Madam Chan.

444
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,000
Madam Chan.

445
00:40:46,200 --> 00:40:47,200
Madam Chan.

446
00:40:47,500 --> 00:40:48,200
Dong.

447
00:40:48,700 --> 00:40:50,200
You frighten me.

448
00:40:51,200 --> 00:40:52,200
I have important matter to discuss.

449
00:40:53,200 --> 00:40:54,200
Why did you tell Madam?

450
00:40:54,600 --> 00:40:57,200
You'd better tell Madam Li and Mr. Tian.

451
00:40:57,700 --> 00:40:59,200
Madam Chan is just a mistress.

452
00:40:59,700 --> 00:41:01,200
Nuan, are you cursing me again?

453
00:41:01,500 --> 00:41:02,200
Huh?

454
00:41:02,900 --> 00:41:03,200
But this is important.

455
00:41:04,200 --> 00:41:05,200
You must be curious for sure.

456
00:41:06,200 --> 00:41:08,200
I don't want to know, I'm busy right now.

457
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:10,200
It's about Mr. Tian.

458
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:16,200
If this leaks out,

459
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:19,200
Mr. Tian will definitely be removed from the leader position.

460
00:41:22,200 --> 00:41:23,200
Do you know the secret already?

461
00:41:24,200 --> 00:41:25,200
What does Tian do?

462
00:41:26,200 --> 00:41:28,200
Tell me now. Tell me now.

463
00:41:30,200 --> 00:41:32,200
Before I got this information,

464
00:41:33,200 --> 00:41:35,200
I had to risk myself as well.

465
00:41:36,200 --> 00:41:38,200
If you have some compensation for me…

466
00:41:42,200 --> 00:41:44,200
Tell me how much you want.

467
00:41:47,200 --> 00:41:48,200
What are you guys doing here?

468
00:42:14,200 --> 00:42:16,200
I called Dong to do something for me.

469
00:42:18,200 --> 00:42:20,200
Dong, let's go that way.

470
00:42:21,200 --> 00:42:22,200
What business do you have with him?

471
00:42:24,200 --> 00:42:27,200
I don't see you do anything every day.

472
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:29,200
Dong.

473
00:42:30,200 --> 00:42:32,200
Come with me. I have a job for you.

474
00:42:33,200 --> 00:42:34,200
Hey, Madam.

475
00:42:34,400 --> 00:42:35,200
Didn't you hear it?

476
00:42:36,200 --> 00:42:39,200
I said I would let him do my job.

477
00:42:40,200 --> 00:42:41,200
Dong.

478
00:42:42,200 --> 00:42:43,200
Who will you choose to listen to?

479
00:42:44,200 --> 00:42:46,200
Me as a first madam?

480
00:42:47,900 --> 00:42:49,200
Or a mistress like her?

481
00:43:05,200 --> 00:43:06,200
Madam Li.

482
00:43:24,200 --> 00:43:26,200
What are we going to do?

483
00:43:26,700 --> 00:43:28,200
What secret is Dong going to tell you?

484
00:43:29,200 --> 00:43:31,200
Let's go eavesdrop.

485
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:50,200
Why does old Jia have to stand guard like that?

486
00:43:54,200 --> 00:43:56,200
What were you going to tell Chan just now?

487
00:44:00,200 --> 00:44:01,200
Why?

488
00:44:01,500 --> 00:44:06,200
You can talk to Chan, but not first madam like me?

489
00:44:09,200 --> 00:44:10,200
Nuan, do you here it?

490
00:44:10,600 --> 00:44:13,200
I can't hear a thing. Do you hear it?

491
00:44:14,200 --> 00:44:16,200
If I hear it, will I ask you?

492
00:44:22,200 --> 00:44:23,200
I told you to speak.

493
00:44:26,200 --> 00:44:30,200
I've heard that Mr. Tian said he was a homosexual.

494
00:44:34,200 --> 00:44:35,200
Madam.

495
00:44:36,200 --> 00:44:38,200
Ten years ago.

496
00:44:39,200 --> 00:44:42,200
Mr. Zhang was condemned for being a homosexual until his life was destroyed.

497
00:44:43,200 --> 00:44:44,200
He died of suicide.

498
00:44:45,200 --> 00:44:46,200
The blood stains are still here until now.

499
00:44:48,200 --> 00:44:49,200
If the truth about Mr. Tian leaks out,

500
00:44:50,200 --> 00:44:51,200
it will be a big deal.

501
00:44:55,200 --> 00:44:57,200
Oh I understand now.

502
00:44:58,200 --> 00:44:59,200
So you rushed to tell Chan.

503
00:45:01,200 --> 00:45:02,200
Madam.

504
00:45:03,200 --> 00:45:07,200
This is bad. He will disgrace the family name.

505
00:45:07,200 --> 00:45:09,200
I'm just worried about Song family.

506
00:45:09,900 --> 00:45:11,200
You are only a worker.

507
00:45:12,200 --> 00:45:14,200
Don't pretend to love and want to protect my family.

508
00:45:16,200 --> 00:45:17,200
As for Tian,

509
00:45:18,200 --> 00:45:19,200
you don't have evidence.

510
00:45:20,200 --> 00:45:23,200
Who would believe a worker like you?

511
00:45:24,200 --> 00:45:25,200
Perhaps,

512
00:45:26,200 --> 00:45:29,200
you could be fired for insulting Tian.

513
00:45:30,200 --> 00:45:32,200
There is no need for evidence.

514
00:45:33,200 --> 00:45:35,200
If I spread this news,

515
00:45:36,200 --> 00:45:38,200
others will find a way to prove the truth.

516
00:45:39,200 --> 00:45:43,200
Whether it is Madam Chan or someone from the Five Dragons Association.

517
00:45:44,200 --> 00:45:47,190
Everyone knew that people in Five Dragons Association aren't that close.

518
00:45:47,200 --> 00:45:49,200
You only think of a way to overthrow each other.

519
00:45:51,200 --> 00:45:54,200
With the scandal of Mr. Tian being a homosexual, a gay,

520
00:45:55,200 --> 00:45:58,200
I think Song family would surely perish.

521
00:46:00,200 --> 00:46:04,200
I assure you that it will be more devastating than Mr. Zhang's scandal.

522
00:46:05,200 --> 00:46:06,200
Dong.

523
00:46:07,200 --> 00:46:08,200
You must have forgotten

524
00:46:09,200 --> 00:46:10,200
that I'm the first madam here.

525
00:46:11,200 --> 00:46:13,200
I have a lot more money than Chan.

526
00:46:15,200 --> 00:46:17,200
How much do you want?

527
00:46:19,200 --> 00:46:21,200
Then shut your mouth tightly.

528
00:46:26,200 --> 00:46:27,200
What are you laughing at?

529
00:46:29,200 --> 00:46:31,200
You offer me the money to cover my mouth like this.

530
00:46:32,200 --> 00:46:34,200
I feel more assured that

531
00:46:34,900 --> 00:46:37,200
Mr. Tian's secret is true.

532
00:46:40,200 --> 00:46:41,200
Thank you, Madam.

533
00:46:43,200 --> 00:46:44,200
Let me think about it first

534
00:46:45,200 --> 00:46:47,200
how much I should take.

535
00:46:59,200 --> 00:47:00,200
Let's go.

536
00:47:18,200 --> 00:47:19,200
Move.

537
00:47:20,200 --> 00:47:21,200
What's the heck?

538
00:47:22,200 --> 00:47:23,200
Mud.

539
00:47:24,200 --> 00:47:25,200
Let's go to the market with me.

540
00:47:25,800 --> 00:47:27,200
Whatever you want, I'll buy it for you.

541
00:47:28,200 --> 00:47:29,200
I'm not going.

542
00:47:30,200 --> 00:47:32,200
I have to stay here to serve Mr. Tian.

543
00:47:32,500 --> 00:47:33,200
In case he requests me.

544
00:47:35,200 --> 00:47:36,200
Mr. Tian?

545
00:47:40,200 --> 00:47:41,200
Mud.

546
00:47:41,900 --> 00:47:44,200
Mr. Tian doesn't like you.

547
00:47:44,900 --> 00:47:46,200
Don't dream too high.

548
00:47:48,200 --> 00:47:51,200
Do you mean that he has a fiancé already?

549
00:47:52,200 --> 00:47:54,200
I already know about that.

550
00:47:55,200 --> 00:47:56,200
But I don't care.

551
00:47:57,200 --> 00:48:00,200
I'd rather be Mr. Tian's mistress than be your wife.

552
00:48:00,400 --> 00:48:01,200
Mud.

553
00:48:02,200 --> 00:48:03,200
I also have money.

554
00:48:03,900 --> 00:48:05,200
How much do you want?

555
00:48:06,200 --> 00:48:08,200
Let go of me. Annoying.

